@startuml
!theme plain
title Fingerprint MIS - Level 0 Data Flow Diagram (Context Diagram)

' External entities
actor Admin as "Admin"
actor Instructor as "Instructor" 
actor Invigilator as "Invigilator"
actor Security as "Security Personnel"
actor Student as "Student"

' Main system
rectangle "Fingerprint Management\nInformation System\n(Fingerprint MIS)" as System

' Data flows from external entities to system
Admin --> System : User Registration Data\nCourse Creation Data\nSystem Configuration\nUser Management Commands
Instructor --> System : Course Data\nAttendance Session Data\nStudent Enrollment Data
Invigilator --> System : Exam/CAT Attendance Data\nInvigilator Activity Data
Security --> System : Security Verification Requests\nAccess Control Data
Student --> System : Registration Data\nFingerprint Template\nCourse Join Requests

' Data flows from system to external entities
System --> Admin : User Reports\nAttendance Reports\nSystem Statistics\nUser Management Results
System --> Instructor : Attendance Reports\nCourse Analytics\nStudent Lists\nAttendance Status
System --> Invigilator : Attendance Reports\nExam Session Data\nActivity Reports
System --> Security : Verification Results\nAccess Decisions\nSecurity Reports
System --> Student : Registration Status\nCourse Enrollment Status\nAttendance Records

' External data stores
database "Firebase\nFirestore" as Firebase
database "Fingerprint\nDevice" as FingerprintDevice

' System interactions with external data stores
System <--> Firebase : User Data\nAttendance Records\nCourse Information\nFingerprint Templates
System <--> FingerprintDevice : Fingerprint Capture\nTemplate Generation\nFingerprint Matching

@enduml
